{
  "stem": "21308.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In fact, we landed where three or four years later, there was a big kommando raid, the greatest raid of all, at Saint-Nazaire, when they drove HMS into the dock gates, the object being to close that port to the German [INAUDIBLE] ships.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then with my division, we went up and took up our positions on the Belgian frontier.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Second Infantry Division.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "16Th Field.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we-- we were a good regiment.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "By now, by working day and night and we had a new CO who drove us along.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were an efficient regiment, a very efficient regiment.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was now Sergeant Major.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had got up-- I was what they call a Warrant Officer, Class III, and my job was with the guns.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And my corps commander was Sir John Dill, who later became Chief of the Imperial General Staff and then he went to Washington as the British representative of the Combined Chiefs of Staff Committee.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he did a great job with the Americans, before the Americans came in.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then they learned enough about him to trust him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In fact, he's buried in Arlington Cemetery in the United States, one of the very few foreigners buried in that-- and they built an equestrian statue.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The Americans put it on his grave.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I have a figure of it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It certainly didn't go how I thought it would.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The-- there was great secrecy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't know what the plans were, we ordinary soldiers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We knew what our tasks were, but we didn't know what the plans were.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the advance to the River Dijle position-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] --well, I mean, we didn't know it.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
